the best fireplace book this is the best fireplace book i have seen . first of all the book has hundreds of beautiful and varied fireplace pictures . the pictures are great because they show the fireplaces in the home , decorated , and with the home furnishings around them . they are all warm and inviting although very different . the text of the book flows well also . first it helps even a novice decorator find the styles that work with your personality and home . then it breaks down fireplace ideas by the different living areas in the house